data.title: Palantir Billionaire Peter Thiel Sells Nvidia and Buys an AI Stock Up 476,900% Since Its IPO
data.description: Hedge fund billionaire Peter Thiel sold his entire stake in Nvidia and started a position in Microsoft during the third quarter.
